e name.  See also  Joss ."],"variants":[]}],"historicEvents":[{"id":1705197,"age":53,"year":"1455","julianDay":2252488,"title":"Wars of the Roses","description":"Wars of the Roses was a series of English civil wars for control of the throne of England between the royal families House of Lancaster and the House of York. The name of the war was derived as the red rose was the symbol of the Lancastrians and the white rose was the symbol of the Yorks.","url":"https://www.history.com/topics/british-history/wars-of-the-roses","urlTitle":"History - Wars of the Roses","jurisdictionLevel":0}],"lifeSummary":"Joyce Westcroft was born about 1402, in England. She had at least 1 daughter with John Wolryche."},"et":{"abt1402–":"umbes 1402–Surnud","1400–Male":"1400–Surnud","1424–Female":"1424–Surnud","1402–Female":"1402–Surnud","1424":"1424","1402":"1402","1455":"1455","1400":"1400","abt1402":"umbes 1402","Shropshire, England":"Shropshire, England","England":"England"},"fi":{"abt1402–":"noin 1402–Kuollut","1400–Male":"1400–Kuollut","1424–Female":"1424–Kuollut","1402–Female":"1402–Kuollut","1424":"1424","1402":"1402","1455":"1455","1400":"1400","abt1402":"noin 1402","Shropshire, England":"Shropshire, England","England":"England"},"fr":{"abt1402–":"environ 1402–Décédée","1400–Male":"1400–Décédé","1424–Female":"1424–Décédée","1402–Female":"1402–Décédée","1424":"1424","1402":"1402","1455":"1455","1400":"1400","abt1402":"environ 1402","Shropshire, England":"Shropshire, Angleterre","England":"Angleterre","lifeSummary":"Joyce Westcroft est née environ 1402, à Angleterre. Elle a eu au moins 1 fille avec John Wolryche."},"de":{"abt1402–":"um 1402–Verstorben","1400–Male":"1400–Verstorben","1424–Female":"1424–Verstorben","1402–Female":"1402–Verstorben","1424":"1424","1402":"1402","1455":"1455","1400":"1400","abt1402":"um 1402","Shropshire, England":"Shropshire, England","England":"England","lifeSummary":"Joyce Westcroft wurde um 1402 in England geboren. Sie hatte mit John Wolryche mindestens 